In more than 65 years of history Fazenda Nossa Senhora Aparecida has always placed among the finalists in Cup of Excellence and also in regional quality competitions. This Brazilian lot sourced in a privileged region of the Mantiqueira de Minas mountains, gives a well balanced cup with good body.  It's sweet with slight acidity.  Flavor profile consists of milk chocolate, vanilla, and nuts.
